  "editorialStatus": "published",
  "reviewOwner": "stuart",
  "formulaSource": "Annual Premium = (Home Value / 1,000 × State Rate) × Deductible Adj × Coverage Adj × Claims Adj × Credit Adj. Rates per $1,000: TX $5.50, FL $8.00, OK $6.00, KS $5.80, CO $4.50, LA $7.50, MN $3.50, CT $3.80, NE $5.00, National Avg $3.50. Source: NAIC, III, Bankrate 2025.",
